headline: Unpacking Q1 Earnings: Lennox (NYSE:LII) In The Context Of Other HVAC and Water Systems Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Lennox (NYSE:LII) and the best and worst performers in the hvac and water systems industry.

headline: A Look Back at HVAC and Water Systems Stocks’ Q1 Earnings: CSW (NASDAQ:CSWI) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
